HEADWORD: re-assess
<hw>re`-as*sess"</hw></mhw> <pos>v. t.</pos>
<def>To revise or renew one's assessment of; <as>as, we need to
<ex>reassess</ex> our position to include the new information</as>.
Usually used without the hyphen.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> re-evaluate, reevaluate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> +<source>PJC</source>]</p>

